#Loan Prediction System
This project is a *Machine Learning* application that predicts whether a loan applicant is eligible for a loan based on
their personal and financial details. It uses historical data to train a classification model to automate the
loan approval process.
#Overview
The goal of this project is to help financial institutions minimize the risk of loan defaults by identifying
high-risk applicants early in the process.
##  Tech Stack
* Language: Python
* Libraries: Pandas (Data Manipulation)
    * NumPy (Numerical Computing)
    * Scikit-Learn (Machine Learning Models)
    * Matplotlib / Seaborn (Data Visualization)

## Dataset Features
The model analyzes the following attributes:
* Gender, Married, Dependents
* Education & Self-Employment status
* Applicant & Co-applicant Income
* Loan Amount & Loan Amount Term
* Credit History
